{"_id":"hxdvxavgy74","name":"Limited Degree","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Your Affliction is limited to no more than two degrees of effect. With two applications of this modifier, it is limited to no more than one degree of effect.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"udfc92kghab","name":"Activation","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>A power with this flaw requires an action to prepare or activate before any of its effects are usable. Move action is –1 point, standard action is –2 points.</p><p>Flat -1 or -2 points.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"6oqbsexu9ub","name":"Instant Recovery","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>The target of an Affliction effect with this modifier recovers automatically, no check required, at the end of the round in which the duration ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"9mk5q1kzsvp","name":"Check Required","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An effect with this flaw requires a check of some sort—usually a skill check—with a base difficulty of 10, +1 for each additional rank in Check Required.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"28e1l4dlh2c","name":"Concentration","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Using a Concentration effect requires more concentration than normal. If you are unable to maintain your concentration, the effect ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"lfshbbofyom","name":"Diminished Range","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the effect’s range increments by one step.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"8idgkhj748e","name":"Distracting","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Using a Distracting effect requires so much concentration or effort that you are vulnerable until the start of your next turn.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"qmc58ysdssk","name":"Grab-Based","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An attack with this flaw requires you to successfully grab and hold a target before the effect can be used.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"zdboclgrba","name":"Increased Action","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw increases the action required to use an effect by one step (Free to Move, Move to Standard, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"pmbnrwpoemq","name":"Limited","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An effect with this flaw only works under certain circumstances, or has a significant restriction on its use.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"58fmpytnujv","name":"Noticeable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>A continuous or permanent effect with this flaw is very noticeable (glows, makes a loud noise, etc.).</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"my98lm3ontq","name":"Quirk","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>A Quirk is a minor flaw, often something specific to a character or power, that doesn’t quite rise to the level of a full -1 cost per rank flaw.</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"e16hm64rxhv","name":"Reduced Range","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the range of an effect (Ranged to Close, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"izt4zzs1oa","name":"Resistible","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An effect with this flaw allows an additional resistance check, or is resisted by a different defense than usual.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"0nt7dpo8yeq","name":"Sense-Dependent","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>The target must be able to perceive the effect with a particular sense for it to work.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"yxsinav02i","name":"Side Effect","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>If you fail to use the effect properly, or even if you succeed, you suffer a negative side effect.</p><p>–1 or –2 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"refeqkyyci","name":"Tiring","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Using the effect is physically or mentally taxing, causing you to become fatigued.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"7o1n42qj3zu","name":"Uncontrolled","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>You have no control over when the effect activates or what it does; the GM decides.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"ovotpibj3yq","name":"Unreliable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An Unreliable effect only works some of the time (5 uses, or requires a check each time).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"kan3tf6y7tq","name":"Feedback","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>You suffer damage when a manifestation of your effect is damaged.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"cvw36geo03a","name":"Inaccurate","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An effect with this flaw is hard to control or wildly inaccurate. Each rank gives you a –2 penalty to attack checks.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"8aocrsvcwdr","name":"Permanent","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>A continuous effect with this flaw becomes permanent in duration. It cannot be turned off and cannot be improved using extra effort.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"d41nneqg0nl","name":"Removable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Removable applies to the power as a whole. The flaw is worth –1 point per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -1 point per 5 points.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"hbmel7i96nl","name":"Easily Removable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An easily removable power can be taken away with a disarm or grab action. The flaw is worth –2 points per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -2 points per 5 points.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":2}}}
{"_id":"ufl001flight","name":"Gliding (Flight)","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>You fly by gliding on wind currents. Your maximum gliding distance is limited to your starting height distance rank plus your flight speed rank. You may be able to gain altitude occasionally by catching a thermal or updraft.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"ufl002healing","name":"Empathic (Healing)","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>When you heal a subject, you take on their damage conditions yourself. Your Toughness cannot resist this damage.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"ufl003healing","name":"Temporary (Healing)","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>The healing you provide is temporary, lasting for only one minute, after which the subject’s damage conditions return.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"ufl004leaping","name":"Full Power (Leaping)","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>You can only leap your maximum distance; you can make shorter leaps only by not using your Leaping effect at all.</p><p>Flat –1 point.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"ufl005teleport","name":"Medium (Teleport)","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>You require a medium (like shadows, mirrors, electricity, etc.) to teleport.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","rang":1,"edit":true,"cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}